<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
I was wondering why I kept getting hit by traps. This is a very nasty bug. 
    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
Detect traps so that the "DTrap" message goes on at the bottom of the map. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
Cast Probability Travel. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
Move out of the detected area by traveling through a wall. 
</p>
</li>

    </ol>


<p>
"DTrap" is still at the bottom of the map, and does not disappear even when you move around in the non-detected area. 
</p>
<p>
<a href="./MassimilianoMarangio">MassimilianoMarangio</a>: Fixed in ToME 2.3.0 
</p>
